8.la: Seuli in Corea, passio sanctorum [todo-1|Sebastiani Nam I-gwan] et novem sociorum*, martyrum, ...; commemorantur item sanctae martyres [2|Lucia Kim], [todo-3|Catharina Yi], vidua, atque ipsius filia [todo-4|Magdalena Cho], virgo, ... occubuerunt.[/][/]*Quorum nomina: sancti [todo-5|Ignatius Kim Che-jun], [todo-6|Carolus Cho Shin-ch'ol], [todo-7|Columba Kim Hyo-im], virgo; [todo-8|Magdalena Pak Pong-son] et [todo-9|Perpetua Hong Kum-ju], viduae; [todo-10|Iulitta Kim], [todo-11|Agatha Chon Kyong-hyob], [todo-12|Magdalena Ho Kye-im].
